### WIMP App REST API — interactive request file
### Works in Visual Studio 2022 (built-in) and VS Code with the REST Client extension.
###
### Typical workflow:
###   1. Run the API:  dotnet run  (starts on http://localhost:5000)
###   2. Register a customer
###   3. Login → copy the token into @token below
###   4. Place orders, deliver them, cancel them, etc.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = PLACE_TOKEN_HERE

# ─── Registration ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Register a new customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Rebecca",
  "email": "rebecca@example.com"
}

###

### Register — invalid email (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Bob",
  "email": "not-an-email"
}

###

# ─── Authentication ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Login (copy the returned token into @token above)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Rebecca",
  "password": "Pa22w0rd!"
}

###

### Login — wrong password (expect 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Rebecca",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### Logout
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ─── Promotions ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Activate the Margherita Friday promotion
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/promotions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Margherita Friday"
}

###

# ─── Orders ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Place a Margherita order (requires login token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    { "name": "Margherita", "size": "Medium", "style": "Regular" }
  ],
  "deliveryAddress": "2-4 Waterloo Pl, Edinburgh EH1 3EG",
  "customerEmail": "rebecca@example.com"
}

###

### Place an order that will be rejected (5 large pizzas)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    { "name": "Pepperoni", "size": "Large", "style": "Regular" },
    { "name": "Pepperoni", "size": "Large", "style": "Regular" },
    { "name": "Pepperoni", "size": "Large", "style": "Regular" },
    { "name": "Pepperoni", "size": "Large", "style": "Regular" },
    { "name": "Pepperoni", "size": "Large", "style": "Regular" }
  ],
  "deliveryAddress": "2-4 Waterloo Pl, Edinburgh EH1 3EG",
  "customerEmail": "rebecca@example.com"
}

###

### Get order by number  (replace 1000 with an actual order number)
@orderNo = 1000

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/{{orderNo}}

###

### Change delivery address (only allowed before pickup)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/{{orderNo}}/delivery-address
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "18 Holyrood Park Rd, Edinburgh EH16 5AY"
}

###

### Cancel an order (sends a notification to the customer)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/{{orderNo}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Deliver an order (triggers Margherita Friday coupon if applicable)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/{{orderNo}}/deliver

###

# ─── Kitchen ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Kitchen: take the next order to work on (FIFO)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/kitchen/take-next-order

###

# ─── Notifications & Coupons ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get cancellation notifications for a customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/Rebecca

###

### Get coupons sent to a customer's email
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/coupons/rebecca@example.com
